ibution>Calif.</us_distribution><discussion>Subspecies luzulifolia occurs from the North Inner Coast Ranges and northern Great Valley through the San Francisco Bay area to the southern South Coast Ranges. Natural hybridization between subsp. luzulifolia and subsp. lutescens has been reported (E. B. Babcock and H. M. Hall 1924).</discussion></treatment>
